    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 GT3, featuring the legendary 3.6L Mezger flat-six power unit. This high-revving, naturally aspirated masterpiece utilizes a true dry-sump lubrication system and remains free of overrevs, as confirmed by a recent DME report. The G96/96 six-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, delivering power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is a marvel of mechanical precision, equipped with adjustable coilovers and monoball suspension links that retain their factory-spec tolerances. With original paint verified by ultrasonic depth gauges and a pristine undercarriage showing no oxidation, this GT3 represents the pinnacle of analog performance and peak mechanical preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
