    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis integrity is flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled VANOS system ensuring peak variable valve timing performance. The limited-slip differential operates with factory precision, and the suspension retains its original damping characteristics without a hint of bushing deflection. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to exceed OEM specifications. This is a rare, turn-key specimen for the discerning collector seeking the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
